main event: A brilliant white light was reported in the sky near Cadillac, Michigan by tourists and police, but Air Force radar and interceptors could find nothing.
interesting points: The object was described as similar to a large light bulb and was white with colored exhaust., The sighting lasted approximately three hours., Multiple radar contacts were made by an F-89 for three seconds each., Witnesses included local police and several tourists from Illinois., The object appeared to ascend and at times give off different colors.
